From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: bobium <dev@bobium.org>
Date: Mon, 1 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] privacy: disable ipv6 reachability probes to google

Chromium periodically sends network probes to google.com to test
IPv6 reachability. This patch neutralizes that behavior to prevent
background pinging.

---
 net/base/network_change_notifier.cc | 3 +++
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+)

diff --git a/net/base/network_change_notifier.cc b/net/base/network_change_notifier.cc
--- a/net/base/network_change_notifier.cc
+++ b/net/base/network_change_notifier.cc
@@ -500,6 +500,9 @@ void NetworkChangeNotifier::NotifyObserversOfNetworkChangeForTests(
 // static
 void NetworkChangeNotifier::StartIPv6ReachabilityCheck() {
+  // bobium: Prevent background pings to Google for IPv6 testing.
+  VLOG(1) << "bobium: IPv6 reachability check blocked.";
+  return;
+
   // Original probe logic...
 }

